OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FChannel Islanders feel their lives are
OL,7,Fgetting worse and they do not have the
OL,8,Fpower to change it, according to a new
OL,9,Fsurvey.
OL,11,FTwo in three Jersey respondents
OL,12,Fbelieve their island is heading in the
OL,13,Fwrong direction, and none of the
OL,14,Fparticipants in Guernsey think
OL,15,Fpoliticians represent them "very well".
