OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FMore than 1,700 people from across the
OL,7,FChannel Islands were surveyed by
OL,8,FIsland Global Research (IGR) and asked
OL,9,Fto share their views on key societal
OL,10,Fissues, as well as the extent to which
OL,11,Fthey trust institutions and
OL,12,Forganisations which deliver essential
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,FWhat did the Jersey figures reveal?
OL,17,FRespondents were asked to choose the
OL,18,Ffive issues facing the island that
OL,19,Fshould be prioritised from a list of
OL,20,F20.
