OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FJust 1% of islanders questioned
OL,7,Fbelieve they influence decisions that
OL,8,Fare made.
OL,10,FMoving on to voting intentions, 46%
OL,11,Fdeclared they will "definitely" cast
OL,12,Ftheir ballot in the next Jersey
OL,13,Felection, while 26% said they will
OL,14,F"probably vote".
OL,16,FFewer than 20% of respondents say the
OL,17,Fpeople who have been elected to make
OL,18,Fdecisions in their island represent
OL,19,Ftheir views and values either "quite
OL,20,Fwell" or "very well".
