OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FWhat did the Guernsey figures reveal?
OL,8,FParticipants in Guernsey highlighted
OL,9,Fthe top concerns for their island,
OL,10,Fpicking out the five issues that
OL,11,Fshould be focused on from a list of 20.
OL,13,FAffordable housing at 68% was the most
OL,14,Fcommon response, 61% included the cost
OL,15,Fof living, and 40% want more focus on
OL,16,Fimprovements to infrastructure.
