OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FMore than three-quarters of those
OL,7,Fsurveyed believe the island is heading
OL,8,Fin the wrong direction and 54% feel
OL,9,Fthey do not influence the decisions
OL,10,Fmade.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, 56% said elected officials
OL,13,Fdo not represent their views and
OL,14,Fvalues.
OL,16,FLooking at the high cost of living, 4%
OL,17,Fsaid they could not afford what they
OL,18,Fspend, and 30% can cover only the
OL,19,Fessentials.
