OL,3,CHeading in the wrong direction:
OL,4,CResidents' views on island life
OL,6,FHowever, more than half describe their
OL,7,Ffinancial situation as "comfortable"
OL,8,Fand 11% as "very comfortable".
OL,10,FReacting to the report, Deputy Chief
OL,11,FMinister Heidi Soulsby says: "It's
OL,12,Fdisappointing to read that, but not
OL,13,Fsurprising.
OL,15,F"I think there's a feeling of
OL,16,Ffrustration that the States hasn't got
OL,17,Fvery far and how it's acted and not
OL,18,Fmade the important decisions."
